#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:1
msgid "回测结果评价与分析"
msgstr "Backtest Results Evaluation and Analysis"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:3
msgid "绩效指标完整列表（罗列并简短解释）"
msgstr "Complete list of performance metrics (list and briefly explain)"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:5
msgid ""
"以下为回测结果中常用或 **evaluate** 可用的指标，与 qteasy 2.0 一致为"
"准。"
msgstr ""
"Below are commonly used metrics in backtest results or those available "
"in **evaluate**, consistent with qteasy 2.0."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "指标"
msgstr "Metrics"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "含义"
msgstr "Meaning"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "总收益 / total_return"
msgstr "Total return / total_return"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "区间累计收益率。"
msgstr "Cumulative return over the period."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "年化收益 / annual_return"
msgstr "Annualized return / annual_return"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "年化后的收益率。"
msgstr "The annualized rate of return."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "夏普比率 / sharpe_ratio"
msgstr "Sharpe ratio / sharpe_ratio"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "风险调整后收益。"
msgstr "Risk-adjusted return."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "最大回撤 / max_drawdown"
msgstr "Maximum drawdown / max_drawdown"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "区间内最大净值回撤。"
msgstr "Maximum net value drawdown within the period."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "胜率 / win_rate"
msgstr "Win rate / win_rate"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "盈利次数占交易次数比例。"
msgstr "The proportion of winning trades out of total trades."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "盈亏比"
msgstr "Profit/loss ratio"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "平均盈利/平均亏损（若有）。"
msgstr "Average profit / average loss (if any)."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "其他"
msgstr "Other"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md
msgid "如 Calmar、波动率等，以 evaluate 输出为准。"
msgstr "Such as Calmar, volatility, etc., refer to the evaluate output."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:17
msgid "可视化"
msgstr "Visualization"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:19
msgid ""
"**visual=True**：在 **qt.run(..., visual=True)** 时，会生成并展示资金曲"
"线、回撤等图。"
msgstr ""
"**visual=True**: When running **qt.run(..., visual=True)**, it will "
"generate and display charts such as the equity curve and drawdown."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:20
msgid "也可单独调用绘图接口（若有），传入结果对象得到相同或更多图表。"
msgstr ""
"You can also call the plotting interface (if available) separately and "
"pass in the result object to get the same or more charts."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:22
msgid "结果导出"
msgstr "Export results"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:24
msgid ""
"将**资金曲线**、**交易列表**导出为 DataFrame 或 CSV：从结果对象中取出对"
"应属性后使用 **to_csv()** 或 **to_excel()** 等。"
msgstr ""
"Export the **equity curve** and **trade list** to a DataFrame or CSV: "
"retrieve the corresponding attributes from the result object, then use "
"**to_csv()** or **to_excel()**, etc."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:25
msgid "便于在外部进行进一步分析或报告。"
msgstr ""
"This makes it easier to perform further analysis or create reports "
"externally."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:27
msgid "简要分析思路"
msgstr "Brief analysis approach"

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:29
msgid ""
"结合 **trade_log** 与**绩效指标**：检查高回撤时段对应的交易、胜率与盈亏"
"比的匹配度。"
msgstr ""
"Combine **trade_log** with **performance metrics**: check the trades "
"corresponding to high-drawdown periods and how well the win rate "
"matches the profit/loss ratio."

#: ../../source/back_testing/5. evaluate_and_analyze.md:30
msgid ""
"可对策略参数、标的池或区间做敏感性分析，或使用《优化交易策略》中的参数"
"优化（mode=2）寻找更优参数。"
msgstr ""
"You can run sensitivity analysis on strategy parameters, the universe, "
"or time ranges, or use the parameter optimization (mode=2) in "
"\"Optimize Trading Strategies\" to find better parameters."
